OL,3,CTwo in five drivers say they have no
OL,4,Calternative to the car for commuting
OL,6,FTwo out of five (40%) drivers say they
OL,7,Fhave no feasible alternatives to the
OL,8,Fcar for getting to work, a new survey
OL,9,Fsuggests.
OL,11,FFor those living in rural locations
OL,12,Fthe figure rises to 70%.
OL,14,FThe RAC, which commissioned the poll,
OL,15,Fsaid the Government is "very focused
OL,16,Fon improving public transport" but its
OL,17,Fresearch shows the car "remains
OL,18,Fcentral to so many people's lives".
