OL,6,FThe RAC said that figure has remained
OL,7,F"remarkably constant" since it began
OL,8,Fasking drivers that question in 1989.
OL,10,FOn Monday, Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,11,FStarmer said it is "extremely hard" to
OL,12,Fbe a motorist "on a modest income".
OL,14,FHe told The Sun that "we need to drive
OL,15,Fdown the cost of motoring", which acts
OL,16,Fas a "lifeline" for many people.
OL,18,FThe RAC survey suggests dependency on
OL,19,Fcars increases with age.
